name: Asset Vault
description: Asset Vault provides utilities to manage funds or assets in DAOs. The company needs to create a vault of investors' addresses mapped with shares (in percent %) according to their investment.

name: DataCV
description: DataCV is a decentralised application that stores data and is based on interplanetary file system(IPFS). It is storage application which comes with top cream privileges. It supports any type of file format.
